1 BUILDING CONSTRUCTION LANDSCAPING SURVEYING BRIDGES BUILD~
New planets are created as they are found with the EXPLORE command. 

In order to build on a planet you must:

A. Belong to the clan the controls the planet.
B. Be "empowered" by your clan to build.
C. Know the building skills/commands...

bridge ....... connects rooms on a planet (skill)
landscape .... used to alter the apearance of a planet (skill)
construct .... build new areas on a planet (skill)
survey ....... get information about a room (skill)

For people desiring to expand their planets heres the advice I offer. Since
you can't delete existing exists, I suggest that you start by building a
road from the colonization center to an new area. You do this by changing
the descriptions and sectors of the rooms with "landscape."  To start
building your new area you use the "construct" comand wich starts a new
room in the direction you supply. Finish that room with "landscape." You
can also use "survey" at any time to get info about a room.  Try to keep
your area well ballanced. Read the help file called "taxes" and check
"showplanet" often.  Remember to build barracks and control towers.
Leaving your area unprotected could result in its capture by opposing
forces and the ultimate destruction of all your hard work. 
~

