1 NEWBIE~
If you are new to mudding this mud might be a liitle difficult to learn on
but I guarantee the experience will be rewarding.

The help files are pretty vague right now but offer a good starting place.
Typing "help" by itself will point you in the right direction.

If you have played any SWR muds before you will notice ALOT of changes in
this version of the code. A major change is how much emphasis is placed
on controling planets and having them almost entirely build by the clans
that control them. Another change you will notice is that spacecraft are
built on demand when you buy them. No more searching around for one for
sale. Just type in the mode you want built for you and voila.

Have fun.
