1 TAXES REVENUE INCOME POPULATION "POP SUPPORT" CITY CITIES FARMLAND WILDERNESS~
Orgizations receive revenue from the planets they control. This revenue is
based on a monthly rate and is paid in hourly installments. The revenue is
generated from a combination of taxes and resource production with
maintenance costs subtracted. The following things affect the total
revenue: 
  
Population...... The higher a planets population the more taxes you receive.
                 A higher population also increases the amount of resources
                 that can be produced. 
Citysize........ Population increases with the size of a city. 
Farmland........ Population is limited based on your food supply. Although
                 food is collected from the wildness, farmland provides a
                 much greater amount. 
Wilderness ..... Areas covered by a planets natural habitat provide a
                 planets total resource base.  

Popular support. The support of the people towards the planets government
                 can drasticly increase or decrease a planets maximum
                 popultaion and thus affect its revenue.

Military........ The cost of supporting a planets military is subtracted.
Automated Ships. The cost of maintaining defensive fleet is subtracted.
Barracks........ The number of barracks on a planet increases the size of a
                 planets army.
Control Towers.. The number of control towers a planet has affects the
                 size of its defensive fleet.
~

